\n。。。。。。<br />\n從業員生計將受影響。<br />\n<br />\n香港資訊科技界工會指，國安法<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n尋釁滋事，或者顛覆國家嘅罪行呢？」<br />\n<br />\n對於早前工會的罷工公投失敗，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n海外組織會向國際展示港人的力量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XbmsRJzeq8qIKRFCUNFvMlTbFfU=/243x162/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X5FOIXISY674AOHEQRTYXMMIDQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXbmsRJzeq8qIKRFCUNFvMlTbFfU%3D%2F243x162%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX5FOIXISY674AOHEQRTYXMMIDQ.gif&h=8bae3c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【日本】&lt;br/&gt;日本駐港總領事館昨日派員接收新工會代表的請願信。&lt;br /<br />\n<br />\n&gt;"},{"pid":"aa6092661431c100c2c63491e4120c33ac248a11","tid":2081365,"uid":186010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:13:49.000Z","msg":"手足堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1640423c9e9ec187095399b2ac6e13be74182b0c","tid":2081365,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:15:24.000Z","msg":"nice move"},{"pid":"8ab9ed15259b1c50bfe3918148ffa7cf023f73d6","tid":2081365,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:34:24.000Z","msg":"入工會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2bad3497a65d589eaeedb11955cf94fc2e1215b","tid":2081365,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:54:54.000Z","msg":"冇宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"8ab9ed15259b1c50bfe3918148ffa7cf023f73d6","tid":2081365,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202